			<p>Elie is a dynamic, versatile and accomplished security risk leader with over 20 years of designing, building, and strengthening security programs at private and publicly traded organizations in highly regulated industries.  He has a long track record of creating security programs from the ground up and is both a technical expert as well as an attorney licensed to practice in State and Federal Courts in Massachusetts. He is an infrastructure and application security subject matter expert with extensive hands-on experience architecting and designing technical and administrative security controls such as SIEM, email security gateways, data loss prevention, database audit monitoring, privileged access management, and data classification.</p>
	
